"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Becoming a successful crypto investor is a long path that requires plenty of learning.  You need to master certain areas, such as investing psychology, history of money, basics of blockchain and cryptography technology. Understanding the short 10 history of the most important crypto project will be of much use as well.\\n\\nOne of the most difficult things for newbies entering the crypto space is finding the signal through the noise. There is absolutely lot of garbage (and outright scams) online. The top priority if you’re serious about learning the fundamentals in the crypto space is to identify what are the most legitimate sources to understand crypto, in it’s basic fundamentals.\\n\\nWhen I started to learn the space, it literally took me 2-3 months to identify what sources should I consume. Now I would like to share the best sources for you to learn.\\n\\nFirst of all, I hope you like reading. Based on my experience, the books are absolutely the best way to build up your fundamental understanding in the shortest amount of time. Forget the crypto news, crypto twitter etc day-to-day content. \\n\\n**Here’s the Top-5 books:**\\n\\n1. Psychology of Money\\n2. Bitcoin Standard\\n3. Infinity Machine\\n4. Layered Money\\n5. The Price of Tomorrow\\n\\n\\n1. Psychology of Money\\n\\n \",\"timestamp\":1637584135,\"title\":\"Becoming a Crypto Investor: My Top 5 Books\"},\"digest\":\"hvuCRkLnCeYCCLGXDG2KU3zTaHO1agFEfjU8ipTpk1o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2b3DaEB14f069dB301cEAD63338a56d27A982CED\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N0cCW28EpD-MB55NohwJeNYT8v92SmdUyiTnxDLe2Pk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xkzdJTJ_7jPlzg4kcaRz53O6hQAD3Hds2UBTCgWsbPs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"M_BqvYQKpL0dsIOhZUIAKE00HkxUiUg2m7UXPDCJa4iFNdz6lTqzq59oHBxEj5mAuHHDQCsnvQm27QOPFstQtQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x79606dd7387d9d3a2303d56e847b19efd1a499e91122824976c65cd09d04644753208ffc2